description:
Comment: Talk given at International Workshop "High-pT physics at LHC" (Tokaj,
  Hungary, March 16-19, 2008); 8 pages including 5 figures as 8 EPS-files;
  prepared using LaTeX package for publication in Proceedings of Science (PoS)

  We analyse the Cauchy problem on a characteristic cone, including its vertex,
for the Einstein equations in arbitrary dimensions. We use a wave map gauge,
solve the obtained constraints and show gauge conservation.
